ροσο</span>  <br id=\"aa-l14-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">14</span>ν καλον μετοπον<span class=\"underline\">καλον</span>  <br id=\"aa-l15-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">15</span>φρυς καλαι οφθαλμ<span class=\"underline\">οι</span>  <span class=\"underline\">καλο</span>  <br id=\"aa-l16-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">16</span>δυο οπα ρεια δυο μυ<span class=\"underline\">κτηρ<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.</span>σ</span>  <br id=\"aa-l17-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">17</span>ομα οδοντες οτα<span class=\"underline\">ρεια</span>  <br id=\"aa-l18-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">18</span>τραχηλες ομοι ακ<span class=\"underline\">ροτερα</span>  <br id=\"aa-l19-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">19</span>κατορυσο <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)</span> σει<span class=\"underline\">σαo<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">..</span>oι</span>  <br id=\"aa-l20-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">20</span>μνημα ειε το επαφρο<span class=\"underline\">δειτον</span>  <br id=\"aa-l21-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">21</span>αλλεια πρειμ<span class=\"underline\">αμ</span>  <span class=\"underline\">τα</span>  <br id=\"aa-l22-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">22</span>υτης την επειστ<span class=\"underline\">ολην</span>  <br id=\"aa-l23-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">23</span>και το ψομ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abb\">face b</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divb--interpretive\">  <a id=\"ab-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]φτηθος <br id=\"ab-l2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]σθοι δυο κ <br id=\"ab-l3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span class=\"underline\">ε</span>να καρδειαν <br id=\"ab-l4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span