σο εις </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"aba\">face a</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"diva--diplomatic\"><a id=\"aa-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ΔΕΟΜΑΙΣΟ<span class=\"underline\"><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·</span>ΚΑ</span><br id=\"aa-l2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΤΟΕΡΜΗΚΑ<span class=\"underline\">ΤΟΧ</span><br id=\"aa-l3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΕΡΜ&nbsp;&nbsp;ΣΟΙΚΑ<span class=\"underline\">Ι</span><span class=\"underline\">ΟΙ</span><br id=\"aa-l4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ΠΟΛΛΟΙΠΑΡΑ<span class=\"underline\">ΙΤΗΤΑΙ</span><br id=\"aa-l5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ΔΕΑΝΙΚΟΝΟΙΤ<span class=\"underline\">ΗΛΚΙ<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·</span>Ε</span><br id=\"aa-l6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>ΔΟΡΕΝΤΟΠΕΜ<span class=\"underline\">ΠΟ</span><br id=\"aa-l7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>ΠΑΔΕΙΚΟΥΜΕ<span class=\"underline\">ΝΗΙΜΑ</span><br id=\"aa-l8-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>ΕΡΟΤΟ<br id=\"aa-l9-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span>ΠΑΔΕΙΣΚΗΝΚ<span class=\"underline\">ΑΛΗΝ</span><br id=\"aa-l10-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">10</span>ΔΟΡΟΥΜΑΙΣΟ<span class=\"underline\">Ι</span><span class=\"underline\">ΚΑΛΟΝ</span><br id=\"aa-l11-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">11</span>ΟΤΑΝΟΕΤΑΤΟΡ<span class=\"underline\">ΑΚΑΛΗ</span><br id=\"aa-l12-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">12</span>ΠΡΕΙΜΑΑΛΛΕ<span class=\"underline\">ΙΑ</span><span class=\"underline\">ΕΧΟΝ</span><br id=\"aa-l13-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">13</span>ΑΤΡΕΙΧΑΣΚΑΛΑ<span class=\"underline\">Σ</span><span class=\"underline\">ΠΡΟΣΟ</span><br id=\"aa-l14-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">14</span>ΝΚΑΛΟΝΜΕ